data.description: You will feel right at home the moment you step into 231 Longleaf Drive. Pride of ownership shines through on this well-cared for 3 bed, 2 bath home! Inside you will find both bathrooms completely remodeled, with dual vanities in the primary bath and dual sinks in the hall bath, giving everyone their own space! The interior also has an updated kitchen with slab granite counters & stainless steel appliances, fresh paint throughout, as well as tile and wood laminate flooring *no carpet*. Walking outside you will discover this peaceful backyard, with a covered patio, an open deck, storage/workshop and a designated space consisting of several garden beds which are ready for planting (they can also be easily removed if you do not have a green thumb). The best part...no rear neighbors!!! This home has never flooded and does not require flood insurance! Schedule your showing today!
